Kaya kong maging pinakamahusay na lalaki

00:32:32.880 --> 00:32:33.440
para sa inyong lahat.

00:32:36.100 --> 00:32:37.460
Hindi pwede.

00:32:37.740 --> 00:32:38.800
Ang galing mo manghuli.

00:32:38.840 --> 00:32:40.520
Pwede kang magpakasal
agad kung gugustuhin mo.

00:32:40.840 --> 00:32:41.320
Eksakto.

